{"tid":641410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英女約難民同遊義大利　反遭囚禁輪姦兩周","createTime":"2018-04-25T03:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T05:26:53.000Z","uid":72009,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"29ee4dc047b930c445a495f828fdec147fce9ba5","tid":641410,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T03:41:24.000Z","msg":"《每日郵報》報導，家住英格蘭北部的39歲女子透過網路，認識居在德國的37歲難民賈洛（Mamadou Jallow）。女子後來飛到德國，想要與他一起生活，但賈洛因為在毒品糾紛中刺傷對手，兩人於是逃離德國，前往義大利。當他們抵達卡拉布里亞省（Calabria）的羅薩爾諾後，賈洛把女子囚禁在偏遠地區一棟房子中，強迫她當性奴。來找來2名難民，一起輪姦女子。<br />\n慘遭輪姦兩周後，女子獲准用電話與家人聯絡，她趁機求救。她的家人再向國際刑警求助，義大利警方追蹤電話來源後，連絡上女子，成功說服、指示她脫困，並逮捕賈洛及另外兩人。賈洛被控涉嫌綁架、奴役、長期性暴力、偷竊及襲擊等罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180425/1341006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180425%2F1341006&d=%2FajnvZ3LkmvwMiyJH2oijBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9f7d3a9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180425%2F1341006&h=f13a5cb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180425/1341006</a><br />\n<br />\n抵死"},{"pid":"6f3180856b3f8cc669f441c443074942b17a012e","tid":641410,"uid":41508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T03:44:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4bbc8d489c3155ccf6db550869e7987dcdfea7b","tid":641410,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T03:48:39.000Z","msg":"爛民都好鍾意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcca20e8aed36cb655b8c6f8dc2f747178dea66","tid":641410,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T03:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 左膠除左俾人奴役仲有乜用"},{"pid":"7381f9c3917e7cc6cf4db9903f556c1693ab8b91","tid":6414